    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this beauty\u2014it\u2019s honestly in such incredible shape, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection inside and out. I'm sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely fall in love with it. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
      "price": 43500.0,
