    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the legendary 4.0L S65 V8 and a precise 6-speed manual transmission. This collector-grade example is in showroom condition, with meticulous maintenance records including preventative rod bearing and throttle actuator service. The chassis dynamics are pristine, utilizing Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a M-Variable limited-slip differential to deliver unparalleled tactile feedback. Free of any mechanical or cosmetic imperfections, this vehicle offers a pure, high-revving 8,400 RPM driving experience that is increasingly rare in the modern market.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
