    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines what it means to be 'pre-owned.' This car is in showroom condition, having been meticulously garage-kept and pampered since day one. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with a professional ceramic coating, completely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no signs of wear or creasing, and it still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver assistance features, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a full documented service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. It has never seen snow or salt, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. Perfect for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
